---
title: Filipino-Inspired Tofu Rice Bowls with Fried Egg and Shallot Rice
description: An homage to one of the quick and functional family-friendly recipes of the Philippines  known as 'giniling,' this is a dinnertime passport to this Southeast Asian paradise.
